ing a core position in property and casualty insurance the firm seeks attractive investment opportunities delegates responsibilities to competent and motivated managers defines risk parameters sets management goals for their operating businesses ensures that managers are provided with incentives to meet these goals and monitors their progress the operating businesses function in an entrepreneurial climate as quasiautonomous enterprises alleghanys management philosophy is conservative they avoid investment fads and fashions in favor of acquiring relatively few interests in basic financial and industrial enterprises that offer the potential to deliver longterm value to the investor executive vice president  chief corporate strategy officer    allied world assurance co holdings ag allied world assurance company holdings ag was established in  today the company employs staff worldwide and offers a mix of insurance and reinsurance solutions to a global clientele allied world maintains offices in atlanta bermuda boston chicago dublin farmington london new york san francisco and zug chief operating officer    allied world insurance co chief financial officer  senior vice president    darwin professional underwriters inc darwin professional underwriters inc provides directors and officers do liability insurance and errors and omissions eo liability insurance for health care professionals and nonmedical professionals it also provides commercial risk management and loss control services for large private companies and public corporations the company was founded in  and is headquartered in farmington ct managing partner    beacon advisors managerbusiness assurance group   prior coopers and lybrand llp coopers  lybrand was the name of one of the predecessor firms which in july  merged with price waterhouse firms to form the global network of pricewaterhousecoopers firms boards  committees corporate boards ▾ chief financial officer director  senior vice president   current darwi